          "Code": "-- 일꾼의 능력치를 레벨에 비례해서 설정해줍니다. -----------------------------------------------------\n\nlocal origin_Speed = tonumber(_DataService:GetCell(\"HelperDataSet\", id, \"speed\"))\nlocal origin_CollectDelay = tonumber(_DataService:GetCell(\"HelperDataSet\", id, \"collectDelay\"))\nlocal speed_Up_Ratio = tonumber(_DataService:GetCell(\"HelperDataSet\", id, \"speed_Up_Ratio\"))\nlocal CollectDelay_Up_Ratio = tonumber(_DataService:GetCell(\"HelperDataSet\", id, \"collectDelay_Ratio\"))\n\nlocal helperLevel = player.PlayerData.Hinventory_Level[self.idx]\n\nself.Speed = origin_Speed + (speed_Up_Ratio * helperLevel) \nself.CollectDelay = origin_CollectDelay + (CollectDelay_Up_Ratio * helperLevel)",
